units       metal

dimension   2
boundary    p p p

atom_style  charge
read_data   graphene.dat

pair_style  reax
pair_coeff  * * ffield.reax 1

variable a1      equal lx/3
variable a2      equal ly/sqrt(3)
variable energy  equal etotal/atoms

fix 1 all deform 1 x erate 1.0 y erate 1.0 remap x

thermo 1
thermo_style custom step etotal pe ke v_energy v_a1 v_a2 pxx pyy

run 2000
